a_T/T from\neach line, the random noise would eventually be reduced down to <~1K and\ndetection of very subtle amount of global T-gradient might be possible.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 3 Aug 2017 12:50:02 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-08-30"}
